{"id":2235,"date":"2024-02-23T01:12:08","date_gmt":"2024-02-22T18:12:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=2235"},"modified":"2024-03-27T11:32:52","modified_gmt":"2024-03-27T04:32:52","slug":"dinh-nui-sam-noi-dau-tien-ba-ngu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/dinh-nui-sam-noi-dau-tien-ba-ngu\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u1ec9nh N\u00fai Sam \u2013 N\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean B\u00e0 ng\u1ef1"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>N\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 (hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 N\u00fai Sam)&nbsp;l\u00e0&nbsp;n\u01a1i t\u00f4n th\u1edd B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, n\u1eb1m \u1edf huy\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang, Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y Nam B\u1ed9. N\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 cao kho\u1ea3ng 237 m\u00e9t v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng s\u00f4ng C\u1eedu Long.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chau-doc-vietnam-02_1693138460.jpeg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"726\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chau-doc-vietnam-02_1693138460.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2252\" style=\"aspect-ratio:4\/3;object-fit:cover\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chau-doc-vietnam-02_1693138460.jpeg 900w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chau-doc-vietnam-02_1693138460-200x161.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chau-doc-vietnam-02_1693138460-600x484.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1eeb sau truy\u1ec1n thuy\u1ebft khi t\u01b0\u1ee3ng B\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&nbsp;9 c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed3ng trinh&nbsp;khi\u00eang xu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n n\u00fai Sam, l\u1eadp mi\u1ebfu linh thi\u00eang v\u00e0 th\u1edd ph\u1ee5ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng B\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ng\u1ef1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam, du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn th\u0103m B\u00e0 \u1edf mi\u1ebfu th\u1edd, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean v\u00eda B\u1ec7 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/be_da_sa_thach_113551294-1.jpeg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"933\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/be_da_sa_thach_113551294-1-1024x933.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2253\" style=\"aspect-ratio:4\/3;object-fit:cover\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i n\u0103m, h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u du kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n, d\u00e2ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y R\u1eb1m th\u00e1ng Gi\u00eang \u00e2m l\u1ecbch h\u00e0ng n\u0103m, khi h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 n\u00fai \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2.jpeg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2-1024x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2254\" style=\"aspect-ratio:4\/3;object-fit:cover\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2-1024x1024.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2-300x300.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2-150x150.jpeg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2-768x768.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2-600x600.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Mieuba2-100x100.jpeg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 c\u00fang t\u1ebf, di\u1ec5u h\u00e0nh, m\u00faa l\u00e2n, m\u00faa r\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i d\u00e2n gian. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng ni\u1ec1m tin, g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u mong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m m\u1edbi an l\u00e0nh, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ea1t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/toan-canh-le-hoi-chua-ba-nui-sam-1.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/toan-canh-le-hoi-chua-ba-nui-sam-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2255\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/toan-canh-le-hoi-chua-ba-nui-sam-1.jpeg 960w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/toan-canh-le-hoi-chua-ba-nui-sam-1-200x133.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/toan-canh-le-hoi-chua-ba-nui-sam-1-600x400.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i t\u00ednh t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o, N\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 c\u00f2n thu h\u00fat du kh\u00e1ch b\u1edfi v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean hoang s\u01a1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed y\u00ean b\u00ecnh. Du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 leo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai, tham quan \u0111\u1ec1n th\u1edd B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 v\u00e0 chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ea3nh quan xung quanh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Visaoviengmieubachua-11.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"647\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Visaoviengmieubachua-11.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2256\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Visaoviengmieubachua-11.jpeg 960w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Visaoviengmieubachua-11-200x135.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Visaoviengmieubachua-11-600x404.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chu\u1ed7i c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng, qu\u1ea7y h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 du kh\u00e1ch. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c c\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0103n \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 mua nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/z5182330679272_acdf7ab8c2a630b078df8751d84a03af.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"960\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/z5182330679272_acdf7ab8c2a630b078df8751d84a03af-1024x960.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2257\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 v\u00e0 l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o quan tr\u1ecdng, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn du l\u1ecbch v\u0103n h\u00f3a h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2258\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/captreonuisam_chaudoc-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn N\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam,&nbsp;mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o,&nbsp;kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p thi\u00ean&nbsp;nhi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0&nbsp;c\u00e1c&nbsp;ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u0103n ho\u00e1 t\u00e2m linh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e3y&nbsp;li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u2013&nbsp;<strong>KDL V\u0103n ho\u00e1 T\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 \u2013 C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam<\/strong>&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh tham quan, c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 (hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 N\u00fai Sam)&nbsp;l\u00e0&nbsp;n\u01a1i t\u00f4n th\u1edd B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, n\u1eb1m \u1edf huy\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang, Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y Nam B\u1ed9. N\u00fai B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":2252,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[83],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2235"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2235"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2235\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2902,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2235\/revisions\/2902"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2252"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2235"}],"wp:term":[{"